caption: The ambiance was relaxing and the smell when you step inside was heavenly, such a soothing environment! Food was delicious! Will visit there again!
Visited this place with Friends. Amazing ambience, Delicious food and mainly very humble owner. Must try for good food experience.

NOT ALL VEGAN. I ordered on door dash thinking because it has vegan in the NAME OF THE RESTAURANT that it would in fact be vegan food. I received naan with real cheese and presumably with real dairy in the bread itself. It has been a really long time since I had dairy and my stomach and morals are really unhappy with me.
